<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{title}}</title>
  {{> favicon}}
  {{> css}}
</head>

<body>
  {{> header}}
  <div class="container-fluid p-0">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid m-0"
          style="background-image: url('img/about.jpg');background-position:50% 0%;background-size:cover;height:600px;">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row py-4 bg-visalia text-white">
      <div class="col text-center">
        <div class="container">
          <h1 class="display-2">The Community</h1>
          <p class="h5 extra-height">
            Park Visalia offers exemplary services and amenities, with a professional care staff to accommodate
            our residentsâ€™ individual needs. We encourage residents to eat well, make new friends, seek out creative
            pursuits, refine skills, revisit old hobbies and discover new passions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row py-4">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <p class="h2 p-4">Services Included in the Monthly Fee</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Three delicious meals daily, plus snacks</li>
            <li>24-hour on-site staffing</li>
            <li>Regularly scheduled resident assessments for care plans</li>
            <li>Weekly housekeeping and laundry service</li>
            <li>All utlities (except phone) including basic cable TV</li>
            <li>Emergency response system (24-hours a day)</li>
            <li>Full calendar of social, cultural, fitness and recreational programs and activities</li>
            <li>Interior and exterior maintenance of all common areas, residences and grounds</li>
            <li>Scheduled group transportation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <p class="h2 p-4">Community Features and Amenities</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Restaurant-style dining</li>
            <li>Entertainment in our multi-purpose areas</li>
            <li>Outdoor space and gardens</li>
            <li>Salon and barber services</li>
            <li>Wi-Fi equipped throughout the community</li>
            <li>Scheduled transportation for medical appointments</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row py-4">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid d-flex align-items-center"
          style="background-image: url('img/food.jpg');background-position:center 100%;background-size:cover;height:600px;">
          <div class="container text-white p-4 text-center" style="background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
            <p class="display-1">Dining Options</p>
            <p class="extra-height">Our team at Park Visalia is committed to providing a nurturing and
              satisfying dining experience with freshly prepared meals with dining options and choices. Special requests
              are welcomed for individual dietary needs. Healthy snacks are also included.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="extra-height">Park Visalia excels in daily engagement with variety, movement, purpose,
            passion and social connections. Our lifestyle program is guided by five core elements:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><span class="h5">MOVE</span> - Our environment encourages residents to be active, keep moving and get
              involved in the community.</li>
            <li><span class="h5">ENGAGE</span> - We encourage physical, mental, social and spiritual development within
              a supportive environment. Our community and holistic programs are specifically designed to promote
              personal engagement in an active life.</li>
            <li><span class="h5">FEEL</span> - We surround ourselves with people who support positive behaviors and
              provide options to better the mind and body.</li>
            <li><span class="h5">CONNECT</span> - We believe communicating among residents, families and staff is
              essential.</li>
            <li><span class="h5">EAT</span> - Fresh ingredients prepared well provide what everyone needs to enjoy
              living each day with joy, purpose and pleasure.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{> scripts}}
  {{> footer}}
</body>

</html>